{"title":"一半儿","authors":["萧丁","江帆"],"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":7,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"一半儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"萧丁 诗 江帆 画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跳蚤打鼓响咚咚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"皂泡轻吹上九重，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南国夜郎欲称雄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美滋滋陶醉在霸权梦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一半儿蠢来一半儿疯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万象之邦把象吞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桑林深处起妖风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湄公河畔布兽踪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么种？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一半儿豺狼一半儿熊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"知是“英雄”与狗熊？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“常胜将军”倒栽葱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蛋壳儿怎能把长城碰！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看尊容，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一半儿青来一半儿肿。（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}